<head>
<title>String Operations</title>
<style>
    table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        width: 70%;
        margin: 20px auto;
    }
    th, td {
        border: 1px solid black;
        padding: 8px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    th {
        background: #007BFF;
        color: white;
